title: Junior Data Scientist
description:
1. Minimum 1 years experience as a data scientist (Fresh grades are welcome)
  2. Min. D3 in Machine Learning, Statistics, Applied Math, or related fields
  3. Excellent understanding of machine learning techniques and algorithms, such as k-NN, Naive Bayes, SVM, Decision Forests, etc.
  4. Having good knowledge of common data science toolkits, such as R, Weka, NumPy, MatLab, etc. Excellence in at least one of these is highly desirable
  5. Great communication skills
  6. Fluent English is a must
  7. Having good knowledge of data visualization tools, such as Tableau, Power BI, D3.js, GGplot, etc.
  8. Proficiency in using query languages such as SQL.
  9. Good applied statistics skills, such as distributions, statistical testing, regression, etc.
  10. Good scripting and programming skills such as Python.
  11. Data-oriented personality.
  12. Having knowledge of Telecommunication Industry is an advantage.

Please apply here : https://nti.co.id/jobs

title: Full Stack Developer / Manager
description:
We are seeking a talented developer and project manager to become my right-hand person. The highest priority is fluency in English – reading, listening, and speaking. This individual must possess strong development skills, either front-end or back-end, and be able to understand project requirements. He/she will need to be able to manage a team of developers and collaborate closely with me on various projects.

Key development skills may include one or more of the following: React.js, Express.js, Node.js, Python, and mobile app frameworks like Flutter or React Native. The candidate must be willing to relocate to Malang city. A competitive salary range of 15 million to 30 million rupiahs is offered, along with benefits like health insurance, IT equipment, paid vacation time – similar to what you'd find in the United States.

The starting date for this full-time position is between mid-April and mid-May.

Below requirements are all a must, so please dont apply unless you fulfil all these criterias:

  • Technical Proficiency: Minimum of 5 years of experience in software development, with expertise in React.js, Express.js, Node.js, Python, Flutter, or React Native.
  • Management Experience: At least 3 years in a leadership or managerial role within a software development team, with a track record of successful project delivery.
  • Language Skills: Must Fluent in English, capable of effective communication in reading, writing, and speaking.
  • Problem-Solving and Analysis: Demonstrated ability in translating client needs into technical solutions and architectural plans, with strong analytical skills.
  • Leadership and Team Building: Proven experience in leading, mentoring, and developing a team, fostering a positive and productive work environment.
  • Adaptability and Relocation: Willingness to relocate to Malang city and adapt to new work cultures and environments.

title: System Network Engineering
description:
• A bachelor's degree in a relevant field such as Computer Science, Information Technology, or Networking.
  • Hands-on experience in designing, implementing, and managing enterprise networks.
  • Experience with network monitoring, performance tuning, and capacity planning.
  • Familiarity with ITIL (Information Technology Infrastructure Library) framework and IT service management processes.
  • Networking Protocols: In-depth knowledge of networking protocols such as TCP/IP, DNS, DHCP, HTTP, FTP, SMTP, SNMP, etc.
  • Network Devices: Proficiency in configuring, managing, and troubleshooting network devices like routers, switches, firewalls, load balancers, VPN concentrators, etc.
  • Routing and Switching: Strong understanding of routing protocols (e.g., OSPF, BGP, EIGRP) and switching technologies (VLANs, STP, EtherChannel).
  • Network Security: Knowledge of network security principles, including access control lists (ACLs), firewalls, VPNs, encryption protocols, intrusion detection/prevention systems (IDS/IPS), and security best practices.
  • Network Monitoring and Troubleshooting: Experience with network monitoring tools (e.g., Wireshark, Nagios, Zabbix) and troubleshooting network-related issues.
  • Wireless Networking: Understanding of wireless networking standards, WLAN controllers, and wireless security protocols (WPA2, WPA3).
  • Network Virtualization: Familiarity with virtual networking concepts, including VLANs, VXLANs, SDN, and virtual networking technologies like VMware NSX or Cisco ACI.
  • Deep understanding about cloud management,Windows , and Linux server
  • Operating Systems:
  • Proficiency in operating systems commonly used in networking environments, such as Linux/Unix and Windows Server.
  • Experience with network-related services like DHCP, DNS, LDAP, NTP, etc.
  • Scripting and Automation:
  • Basic scripting skills in languages like Python, Bash, or PowerShell for automation tasks, configuration management, and orchestration.
  • Problem-Solving: Ability to analyze and solve complex network-related problems efficiently.
  • Communication: Strong verbal and written communication skills for collaborating with team members, documenting network designs, and communicating with stakeholders.

title: Hydrogeologist - Mining Industry
description:
• Bachelor's or Master's degree in Geology-Hydrogeology, Mining or Civil Engineering (Water Infrastructure)
  • Minimum years of experience in related position; have worked in a mine or feasibility study project of mineralization systems of Indonesia as a Hydrogeologist
  • Have familiar with government regulations and technical requirements permitting for river diversion, Dam and Tailing Storage Facilities (TSF) concept
  • Have strong knowledge of hydrological and hydrogeological modeling in GIS, HEC-RAS, HEC-HMS, FeFlow, and Visual Modflow, and have a familiar understanding of block models and Leapfrog
  • Have strong hydrological, hydrogeological, geological, and mining background with deep concepts about hydro-fracturing/fracture medium in porphyry and epithermal systems, and the alteration/mineralization processes and controls
  • Have good understanding of aquifer tests for hydrogeological properties, rainfall analysis, estimate water balance, dewatering program, and reporting including skill in QA/QC validation process
  • Have experience with planning and execution of geophysical survey activity (example: Resistivity Study)
  • Demonstrate Open and Transparent Dialog
  • Strong teamwork and ownership
  • Health and Safety highly oriented
  • Good level of English language (writing and speaking), and
  • Demonstrate good leadership skills

title: Tax accountant
description:
Untuk melamar posisi tax accountant umumnya dibutuhkan gelar di bidang akuntansi, keuangan, atau bidang lain yang relevan seperti administrasi bisnis dan bisnis. Sertifikasi Certified Public Accountants (CPA) dan Certified Management Accountants (CMA) menjadi nilai tambah dalam peran ini.

Pengetahuan tentang prosedur akuntansi dan pembukuan menjadi kebutuhan seorang tax accountant. Mereka juga harus memiliki keakraban dengan perangkat lunak akuntansi seperti Accurate, Xero, dan Fresh Books. Selain itu, pengoperasian microsoft excel dan perhitungan matematika yang kuat sangat penting.

Di samping itu, soft skill yang dibutuhkan tax accountant adalah keterampilan analitis, manajemen waktu yang sangat baik, dan perhatian yang tajam terhadap detail. Keterampilan dalam mengatasi masalah secara metodis dan pikiran yang terorganisir juga membantu kesuksesan tax accountant.

title: SAP Principal / Senior Consultant / Consultant - Finance (FI, CO, PS)
description:
Qualifications and Skills for FICO:

  • A degree in account or business preferable, alternatively any other science topic.
  • Application is open for all levels (SAP Principal / Senior Consultant / Consultant)
  • At least 8 years of professional experience in the area of Finance and Controlling and understanding integration topics to other modules.
  • Hands-on project experience in S/4HANA is an advantage.
  • Knowledge in programming languages such as ABAP is an advantage.
  • Fluent in English (verbal and written).

Qualifications and Skills for PS:

  • Minimum of 8 years of hands-on experience as an SAP Project System Consultant, with a focus on the Construction and Energy sectors.
  • In-depth knowledge of SAP Project System (PS) modules, including configuration, customization, and integration with other SAP modules.
  • Proven track record of leading successful end-to-end SAP PS implementation projects, including solution design and post-implementation support.
  • Strong understanding of project management principles, processes, and methodologies.
  • Experience with SAP S/4HANA is preferred.
  • Excellent problem-solving skills and the ability to navigate complex technical challenges.
  • Exceptional communication and interpersonal skills to effectively engage with clients and cross-functional teams.


ME: This is you

  • An analytical and problem-solving consultant with the desire to develop your own skills and talents.
  • An eloquent and extroverted person happy to support our pre-sales cycle.
  • Passionate and determined while appreciating teamwork.
  • Willing to take over responsibility and to make decisions.
  • Able to lead a small team, with strong social and communication skills.

WE: That's us
  • A great team of passionate consultants.
  • Strong personalities that are fair, open, and respectful to each other.
  • Attractive and competitive salary and package.
  • A company that continuously spends more than 6% of its revenue in the education of its employees.


Interested in sharing the ONE passion?

We’d love to hear from you! Don’t hesitate to contact us by phone, email or LinkedIn. We look forward to receiving your application documents, which should include your résumé (along with project descriptions), salary expectations, and references (if available). If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us.
